import React from 'react'; import ScoreDisplay from './ScoreDisplay'; import { AddressAnalysisResponse } from '../types/address-analysis'; interface ResultsDisplayProps { results: AddressAnalysisResponse; } const ResultsDisplay: React.FC = ({ results }) => { const { overallScore, mobility, livability, emergency, grocery } = results; return (
  • Transit Station: {mobility.details.station.score}/100 {mobility.details.station.nearest && ` - Nearest: ${mobility.details.station.nearest.name} (${mobility.details.station.distance}m away)` }
  • Bus Stop: {mobility.details.busStop.score}/100 {mobility.details.busStop.nearest && ` - Nearest: ${mobility.details.busStop.distance}m away` }
  • Road Access: {mobility.details.road.score}/100 {mobility.details.road.nearest && ` - Nearest: ${mobility.details.road.nearest.name} (${mobility.details.road.distance}m away)` }
  • Retail: {livability.categoryScores.retail.score}/100 ({livability.categoryScores.retail.count} places)
  • Restaurants: {livability.categoryScores.restaurant.score}/100 ({livability.categoryScores.restaurant.count} places)
  • Entertainment: {livability.categoryScores.entertainment.score}/100 ({livability.categoryScores.entertainment.count} places)
  • Parks: {livability.categoryScores.park.score}/100 ({livability.categoryScores.park.count} places)
  • Schools: {livability.categoryScores.school.score}/100 ({livability.categoryScores.school.count} places)
); }; export default ResultsDisplay;
